nFibNew: An unsigned integer that specifies the version number of the file format that is used. This value MUST be one of the following : 0x00D9, 0x0101, 0x010C, 0x0112
rgCswNewData: Depending on the value of nFibNew this is one of the following : 0x00D9, 0x0101, 0x010C
rgCswNewData_extend: Extension of rgCswNewData if nFibNew is 0x0112, you have to reconstitute rgCswNewData in that case
